channel.title: Need help jarring a client so it can be a webclient! Will pay if it works good!
channel.description: I have been trying to do it myself but my head is about to explode. I got a jar made and everything but it said "Error Loading-please report!) I think what I did wrong is I didn't change the cache download link in the cachedownloader, because the link in there was broken, and I have no idea how to put a cache onto a website.(Trying to figure this out also almost made my head explode.) So if someone could please help me I would be very grateful and if the webclient works fine and everything I will pay you! Please add my MSN: gabrielthomashall@gmail.com
